---

<Layout title="Home" pageTitle="Home" description="Welcome to Iza's Nailtech Art Studio!">
	<Section class:list={"relative"}>
		<Picture
			src={CatBackground}
			alt="Cat"
			class:list={"absolute inset-0 w-full h-full object-cover"}
			loading={"eager"}
			fetchpriority={"high"}
		/>
		<div class="bg-gradient-to-r from-fuchsia-500/60 to-teal-500/80 absolute inset-0"></div>
		<Container class:list={"relative z-10 h-full lg:min-h-svh lg:h-svh"}>
			<div class="flex items-center h-full">
				<div class="ml-auto">
					<div class="prose prose-xl prose-invert text-white lg:text-right text-balance">
						<h1 class="text-5xl lg:text-8xl mb-0">Welcome to Iza's Nailtech Art Studio!</h1>
						<p class="magical">
							We have a variety of pets available for adoption. Please take a look at our available pets
							and contact us if you are interested in adopting one. We are always looking for loving homes
							for our pets. Thank you for considering adoption!
						</p>

						<div class="not-prose mt-8">
							<Button url="/cats" color="white"> Adopt now! </Button>
						</div>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
		</Container>
	</Section>

	<Section class:list={"bg-white"}>
		<Container>
			<Hero>
				<div slot="hero-content-left" class="prose">
					<h2 class="h2 text-teal-500">Book your Nail Transformation Today</h2>
					<p class="leading-loose">
						Explore our exclusive range of nail art stylesâ€”each design created to elevate your look and express your individuality. âœ¨ Browse our portfolio and get in touch to reserve your appointment. We canâ€™t wait to bring your dream nails to life. Thank you for choosing elegance at your fingertips! ðŸ’–
					</p>

					<div class="not-prose mt-16">
						<Button url="/cats">
							<svg
								xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
								class="inline-block size-5 -mt-1 mr-1"
								viewBox="0 0 14 14"
								><path
									fill="currentColor"
									fill-rule="evenodd"
									d="M1.777.053A.5.5 0 0 1 2.3.1l3.917 2.947a6.6 6.6 0 0 1 1.564 0L11.7.1a.5.5 0 0 1 .801.4v8.25h.748a.75.75 0 0 1 0 1.5h-.81a4.5 4.5 0 0 1-.479 1.391l1.376.688a.75.75 0 1 1-.67 1.342l-1.654-.827A4.48 4.48 0 0 1 8 14H6a4.48 4.48 0 0 1-3.011-1.156l-1.654.827a.75.75 0 1 1-.67-1.342l1.376-.688a4.5 4.5 0 0 1-.479-1.391h-.81a.75.75 0 0 1 0-1.5H1.5V.5a.5.5 0 0 1 .277-.447M9.124 7.75a.75.75 0 1 0 0-1.5a.75.75 0 0 0 0 1.5m-4.25 0a.75.75 0 1 0 0-1.5a.75.75 0 0 0 0 1.5m.897 1.605A.5.5 0 0 1 6.25 9h1.5a.5.5 0 0 1 .277.916l-.75.5a.5.5 0 0 1-.554 0l-.75-.5a.5.5 0 0 1-.202-.56Z"
									clip-rule="evenodd"></path></svg
							>
							Adopt a cat
						</Button>
					</div>
				</div>
				<div slot="hero-content-right" class="-rotate-1">
					<Image src={CatOne} alt="Cat" class:list={"w-full h-full object-cover rounded-2xl shadow"} />
				</div>
			</Hero>
		</Container>
	</Section>

	<Section>
		<Container>
			<Heading>
				<h2 slot="heading-title" class="h2 text-teal-500">Featured Nail Art Styles</h2>
				<p slot="heading-content">
					Discover our curated collection of signature nail designsâ€”each crafted with precision, creativity, and a touch of glam. âœ¨ Take a look at our latest styles and get inspired for your next appointment. Weâ€™re here to help you find the perfect look that suits your personality. Thank you for letting us be part of your beauty journey!
				</p>
			</Heading>

			<ShowCats cats={["reckoning", "chairman-meow", "pawdre-hepburn"]} />
		</Container>
	</Section>

	<Section class:list={"bg-white"}>
		<Container>
			<Hero invert>
				<div slot="hero-content-left" class="prose">
					<h2 class="h2 text-fuchsia-500">FAQ</h2>
					<Faq items={faq} color="fuchsia" />
				</div>
				<div slot="hero-content-right" class="rotate-1">
					<Image src={CatTwo} alt="Cat" class:list={"w-full h-full object-cover rounded-2xl shadow"} />
				</div>
			</Hero>
		</Container>
	</Section>

	<Section class:list={"relative"}>
		<Image src={CatBackground} alt="Cat" class:list={"absolute inset-0 w-full h-full object-cover"} />
		<div class="bg-gradient-to-r from-fuchsia-900/80 to-teal-900/80 absolute inset-0"></div>

		<Container class:list={"relative z-10"}>
			<CallToAction
				title="Ready for Gorgeous Nails? Reserve Your Spot"
				link={{ title: "Adopt", url: "/cats", color: "white" }}
			/>
		</Container>
	</Section>

	<Section>
		<Container>
			<Heading>
				<h2 slot="heading-title" class="h2 text-teal-500">Studio Journal</h2>
				<p slot="heading-content">
					Welcome to our blogâ€”your go-to source for the latest trends, updates, and inspirations from our nail art studio. ðŸ’… We're passionate about creativity, self-expression, and elevating beauty through the art of nails. Here, weâ€™ll share behind-the-scenes moments, style tips, artist spotlights, and more. Thank you for being part of our journey and supporting the beauty of individualityâ€”one nail at a time.
				</p>
			</Heading>

			<ShowBlogs posts={["hello-world", "new-arrival-luna", "new-site-launched"]} />
		</Container>
	</Section>

	<Section class:list={"relative"}>
		<Image src={CatBackground} alt="Cat" class:list={"absolute inset-0 w-full h-full object-cover"} />
		<div class="bg-gradient-to-r from-fuchsia-900/80 to-teal-900/80 absolute inset-0"></div>
		<Container class:list={"relative z-10"}>
			<CatNameGenerator title="Help Me Pick a Surprise Style!" />
		</Container>
		<script>
			import { gsap } from "gsap";
			import { SplitText } from "gsap/SplitText";
			console.log("GSAP loaded", gsap.version);
			gsap.registerPlugin(SplitText);

			document.fonts.ready.then(() => {
				// Split the text into words
				let split = SplitText.create(".magical", {
					type: "chars, lines, words",
					onSplit: (self) => {
						gsap.from(split.chars, {
							y: 100,
							autoAlpha: 0,
							stagger: 0.05,
						});
					}
				});
			});

			let split = SplitText.create(".magical", {
				type: "chars, lines, words",
			});
			gsap.from(split.chars, {
				y: 100,
				autoAlpha: 0,
				stagger: 0.05,
			})
		</script>
	</Section>
</Layout>
